{"tid":1333421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【轉自絕食者tg】陳伯同咁多位絕食者有野講啊","createTime":"2019-07-19T16:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T12:52:15.000Z","uid":281064,"like":81,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"689ee0b0673a4b4be44ce0f6c95339680ad4646c","tid":1333421,"uid":281064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:30:44.000Z","msg":"原來政事台冇時事台咁多人睇 呢邊都post翻先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見條片post左一個晏就但都係唔係好多view<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢地呼籲既對象唔係年輕人 希望各位巴絲可以幫手傳出去比長輩們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好多謝一班咁明白事理又願意守護年輕人既長輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【守護孩子，齊來抗爭】行動<br />\n<br />\n75媽媽集會、714陳伯到沙田前線行動守護、715絕食同行苦行禮賓、717銀髮族遊行，顯示抗爭正凝聚各年齡各界別人士，一齊對準政權出發。呼籲你721繼續出泥聲援，遊行完勿散，到金鐘海富共商對策，於當晚如何守護年青人，繼續抗爭！<br />\n<br />\n日期：7月21日(日)<br />\n時間：遊行完(約晚上6至7時，到時決定，有人會在場的簡介)<br />\n集合地點：海富絕食站(金鐘a出口)<br />\n特別邀請參與對象：媽媽、銀髮族、傷健人士、神職人員、社工、律師<br />\n內容：共商方法，然後行動<br />\n*參加者請穿白衫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S_OdJcOCNHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS_OdJcOCNHk&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J8jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=b965441c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S_OdJcOCNHk</a><br />\n<br />\n同場仲有長輩用文宣圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n齊齊落去貼比長輩知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vRLQ4c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvRLQ4c8.png&h=8ddfe971&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xX20GZO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxX20GZO.png&h=1943115e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60f8a43ee7d8dea1b86f57c7301ed8e31a7f4532","tid":1333421,"uid":281064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:30:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fd9de06109941c6b7ebc785590a17756289b3a","tid":1333421,"uid":11804,"like":0,"dislike":74,"score":-74,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:32:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f22f14da432ea79d8608030d2c981c89b787357","tid":1333421,"uid":281064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:32:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a61fe712281cf970685bf4492c6e5e126f7dad61","tid":1333421,"uid":281064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:33:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92d6f592cea1eb65a9ba58281ded0a0513c7b689","tid":1333421,"uid":216364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:34:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都係搞唔掂屋企人但係希望大家啲屋企人會明白然後出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a21f3f4769818d628e42944f46e56079f09daff","tid":1333421,"uid":281064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92d6f592cea1eb65a9ba58281ded0a0513c7b689","tid":1333421,"uid":216364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:34:09.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都係搞唔掂屋企人但係希望大家啲屋企人會明白然後出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"係啊所以幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />相信總有人屋企會支持既"},{"pid":"44aea465866f7d0228db3c9c8bfb4a22d94d9007","tid":1333421,"uid":281064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:36:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"deeaa7857e468344634c8bb68e1ef8859aafd269","tid":1333421,"uid":281064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:37:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9267ac058b8f4756036f441515c14eebfcd80820","tid":1333421,"uid":253127,"like":1,"dislike":